Refer to the CnEcHtml_Colors category of global constants.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <PrimAttribute name="tableHeight" id="82309c87-6d7d-41dc-a120-c94940c07167">
        <length>31</length>
        <embedded/>
        <type name="String"/>
        <text>Specifies the height of the table or row as either a certain number
if pixels or a percentage of the window by appending a percentage
